OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNigerian volunteer:        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'Fighting in Ukraine is    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbetter than living here'   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When Russia launched its invasion of   
OL,6, Ukraine last month, 27-year-old        
OL,7, Nigerian Ottah Abraham was outraged.   
OL,9,FHe picked up his phone and tweeted: "I 
OL,10,Fwant to join the team."                
OL,12,FHe was some 8,700km (5,400 miles) away 
OL,13,Ffrom the front line, in a small        
OL,14,Fapartment in Nigeria's main city,      
OL,15,FLagos.                                 
OL,18,F"We know that it's war, it's not       
OL,19,Fchild's play," he told the BBC. "But   
OL,20,Fbeing a soldier in Ukraine would be    
OL,21,Fbetter than being here.                
